    <div class='update_description'><i onclick="document.location='8653#1275493087'; reset_anchor();" class="pull-right icon icon-share"></i><div class="header"><time datetime="2010-06-02T15:38:07+00:00">Jun 2, 2010 03:38 PM UTC</time> by <b>Neha Sharma</b><a class="anchor" name="1275493087">&nbsp;</a></div><pre>Hi Sarah,

The export &#34;path&#34; simply is a prefix for what you are exporting. In your config file you have exported &#34;/xrdfs/&#34; therefore the minimum valid &#34;path&#34; you
can specify is exactly what you exported... &#34;/xrdfs/&#34;. This is why you get an error when you try to reference &#34;/xrdfs&#34; because it was not exported.

Andy

