No matching files were found.

[root@iut2-dc1 ~]# /opt/xrootd/xrootd/bin/xrd iut2-dc1.iu.edu&#58;1094
locateall /xrdfs/

Charles also noticed last night when he tries to stat /xrdfs using the
posix module, he gets permission denied. But he can stat /xrdfs/.

